═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
PRICE PARSING RULES
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

• "50k" → 50000
• "$500" → 500
• "₦50,000" → 50000
• "500 naira" → 500
• Remove currency symbols and commas

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
MODULE BOUNDARIES (DO NOT CROSS)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

If user mentions:
• Customers → REJECT (wrong module)
• Invoices, sales → REJECT (wrong module)
• Payments → REJECT (wrong module)
• Expenses → REJECT (wrong module)

Return:
{
    "extracted_data": {},
    "confidence": 0.0,
    "missing_required": [],
    "clarification_needed": null,
    "validation_errors": ["Request is outside INVENTORY module scope"]
}
